title: The Jboy Show - Week 4 Recap: Chaos in College Football returns
itunes:title: The Jboy Show - Week 4 Recap: Chaos in College Football returns
description:
Jboy breaks down a stacked week 4 in college football. Jake tells you why LSU's win was so important (2:40), Auburn comeback win and QB controversy (12:30) and Arkansas' upset over Texas A&M (28:00) Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms!
